## Git Workflow

```
main branch        -- Eva's code
partner-dev branch -- Partner's code
```

### Partner Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Anonymous2578/fm-subtype-discovery.git
cd fm-subtype-discovery
git checkout -b partner-dev
```

### Daily Commit Pattern
```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Day X: description of what was built"
git push origin partner-dev
```

### Eva Reviews Partner Code Daily
```bash
git fetch origin
git diff main origin/partner-dev
```

### Day 5 Merge
```bash
git checkout main
git merge partner-dev
# Fix any conflicts
git push origin main
```

